  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The Nintendo DS version of Call of Duty: Black Ops has many new features like the Perks system for the six player online multiplayer. The player can tap an icon to switch the current weapon for a new one, like past DS games, or drag the weapon into an inactive button to add to their inventory without replacing the weapon they are using currently. An auto lock-on feature is available to use in the Recruit and Regular difficulties.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
